// Print Diamond Outline 5 (#1290)

// No input. Prints a 5-row outline-only diamond: rows ` * `, `* *`, ` * ` for top half mirrored... wait the precise pattern: row 1 `  *  `, row 2 ` * * `, row 3 `*   *`, row 4 ` * * `, row 5 `  *  ` (5×5 grid, only outline cells are `*`, others are space).

main

def main {
    stl.startup
    stl.output "  *  \n * * \n*   *\n * * \n  *  \n"
    stl.loop
}
